name: Water Margin(ShuiHu)-art by DaiDunbang
description:
The material comes from the portrait painting by Chinese painter Dai Dunbang for the Chinese literary work "Water Margin". This is my first attempt to train the LORA model myself based on the tutorial, only for learning purposes.
